## Developement Log
- Added CSS grid for UI arrangement
- Implemented a max score and a way to check the score
- Retained score in local client storage to keep score through session
    This could result in cheating so remove the local storage or secure it
    after implementing long term storage of scores
- Added a manual save button
- on load we load the users data from database
- every 30 seconds with interval we check if there are unsaved changes and 
  if none then we don't save, this saves on operations, otherwise we save the data
- Removed local client storage to secure it
- Extracted Double costs to global constant so array doesn't need to be made every time we double
- Instead of creating a new record each save we use the user_id foreign key to updateOrCreate
   this way the users data is updated on saves reducing the memory cost
